23ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5640, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2572 Grade: Mutaffaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8085,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/believer-mirror-to-brother\/","url_meta":{"origin":18801,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ikhwah: Believer is a mirror to his brother","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is a mirror to his faithful brother. He protects him against loss and defends him behind his back.\u201d Abu Huraira said, \"The believer is a mirror to his brother. If he sees something wrong in him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28825,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/08\/parable-believer-horse-stable\/","url_meta":{"origin":18801,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Parable of the believer is a horse in a stable","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon, him, said, \u201cThe parable of the believer and faith is that of a horse in its stable. It roams about and then returns to its stable. Verily, the believer becomes negligent and then returns back to faith.\